name: Analog Surf (Music Video)
description:
Fourth and last drop of the Analog Surf Collection. Video was made using analog extracts from different surf videos. Effects were generated by a variety of analog gear. 

Music was produced using:
ableton daw
giannini super sonic guitar
hall of fame reverb
boss blues driver
boss dd7 delay
peavey rage 158 amp
shure SM57 mic
golden age 73 mkiii pre amp 
focusrite interface

.MP4 // 800X600px
